title: DEWALT Reverse Ratcheting Combination Wrench 5/8" SAE
features: 13 degree offset box end for knuckle clearance
Sizes stamped twice on both sides of wrench handle for easier size identification
15 degree offset open end allows for an increased range of arc swing in tight spaces
DirectTorque Technology helps prevent rounding of fasteners
Stamped markings provide permanent visibility and prevents wear over time.
description: The Reversible Ratcheting Combination Wrench has 72 teeth for a 5 degree arc swing. This wrench has DirectTorque technology to help prevent rounding of fasteners. This wrench also has its size stamped twice on both sides of the handle to make it easy to locate within a tool box.
